---
// FocusAreas.astro
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-50 to-white" id="focus-areas">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
          Real AI Solutions for
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-cyan-500 to-accent-lime-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Real Business Challenges
          </span>
        </h2>
        <div class="w-32 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-cyan-500 to-accent-lime-500 rounded-full mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Focus Areas Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- AI Tools for SMBs -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-accent-lime-200">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-lime-400 to-accent-lime-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-0 mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 7.172V5L8 4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900">AI Tools for SMBs</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Discovering and evaluating AI tools that deliver real value for small and mid-sized businesses. We'll share hands-on experiences with tools that solve common SMB challenges, discuss ROI and implementation realities, and help you cut through the noise to find solutions that actually fit your business needs and budget.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Practical AI Implementation -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-accent-cyan-200">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-cyan-400 to-accent-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-0 mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900">Practical AI Implementation</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Moving beyond generic advice to develop AI practices that work with real SMB constraints: limited technical resources, smaller teams, and tighter budgets. Learn approaches that don't require a dedicated AI team or massive infrastructure investment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Strategic AI Pilots -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary-200">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-0 mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900">Strategic AI Pilots</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Designing AI initiatives that align with core business objectives rather than chasing trends. We'll focus on identifying genuine use cases, setting measurable success criteria, and building pilots that prove value before scaling—helping you avoid costly experiments that don't deliver results.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Risk Management & Governance -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-accent-lime-200">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-lime-400 to-accent-lime-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-0 mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900">Risk Management & Governance</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Understanding AI risks and building practical data governance policies that protect your business without stifling innovation or productivity. Create frameworks that keep your sensitive data secure while enabling your team to leverage AI tools effectively.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Adoption & Change Management -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100 hover:border-accent-cyan-200 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-cyan-400 to-accent-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-0 mr-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900">Adoption & Change Management</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Overcoming staff resistance, building sustainable AI usage habits, and managing the human side of AI implementation—from addressing job security concerns to creating early wins that drive broader adoption and lasting organizational change.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>